價","box":[[117,1286],[895,1288],[895,1309],[117,1307]]},{"text":"還），中國的外匯很聚張（见表8-4）【2]","box":[[113,1326],[547,1320],[547,1353],[114,1360]]}],"dimensions":{"height":1531,"width":1019}}